<template>

  </template>
  
  <script>
  import { mapState, mapActions } from 'vuex';
  
  export default {
    computed: {
      ...mapState(['products', 'users']),
    },
    mounted() {
      this.fetchProducts();
      this.fetchUsers();
    },
    methods: {
      ...mapActions(['fetchProducts', 'fetchUsers']),
    },
  };
  </script>
